# Safety-hook frame mesh (D-shape body, NO gate).
# Units: meters. Coordinate frame: X right (+X = gate side), Y out of plane, Z up.
# Overall dims: ~0.070 wide x 0.020 thick (Y) x 0.150 tall.
# The gate hinge seat is at the top-right: approx (0.030, 0, 0.140).
# The nose (gate tip seat) is at the bottom-right: approx (0.030, 0, 0.010).
# All faces are triangles, CCW winding.

o frame

